subject: NCAA Basketball Championships (Women)
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Tiffany Bias’s driving layup with 41 seconds remaining in overtime lifted No. 5 seed Oklahoma State to a 61-60 victory over No. 12 seed Florida Gulf Coast.
